OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome heavy
OL,6,Fand thundery showers at first, these
OL,7,Fslowly dying out during the evening. A
OL,8,Fdry night with clear spells and
OL,9,Fbecoming rather chilly again.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FA dry and sunny start then
OL,12,Fcloud bubbling up through the morning
OL,13,Fwith showers developing. Some showers
OL,14,Fcould be heavy and thundery in the
OL,15,Fafternoon.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,18,FCloudy with outbreaks of rain on
OL,19,FThursday. Mainly dry with sunny spells
OL,20,Fon Friday and Saturday and becoming
OL,21,Fwarmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
